<H1><A NAME="SECTION00040000000000000000">
Implementation</A>
</H1>

<P>
IDebug is freely available from the <A NAME="tex2html7"
  HREF="http://www.kindsoftware.com/products/opensource/">KindSoftware's
  Open Source web pages</A>.

<P>

